title: in-class Exercise 3
text:
Installing and loading R packages
Two packages will be installed and loaded
They are ggraph and tidyverse

pacman::p_load(tidyverse,ggraph)

import data

exam_data <- read.csv("/Users/chenyiman/ChenYiman/demo0115/ChenYiman98/0122VAA/inclass/data/Exam_data.csv")


ggplot(data= exam_data,
          aes(x = MATHS))+
    geom_dotplot(dotsize = 0.5)
